D&rsquo;Antoni on what makes Shumpert a strong on-ball defender:<br />
<br />
&ldquo;It&rsquo;s toughness. He anticipates well. He gets into people. His determination is huge. Most of the time, you can be a good defender if you want to be. ... He&rsquo;s decided he wants to be a good defender, and he is.&rdquo;

More Morey on Shumpert:<br />
<br />
&ldquo;One thing that really attracted us is when he has played next to a great player, like obviously he will here [Harden] or with a LeBron, he&rsquo;s been one of the top, top guys in the league. He just fits so perfectly working with those top players.&rdquo;
